### TiendaBox - Pruebas del recurso Cart
### Todas las rutas requieren auth + rol "cliente".
### Antes de ejecutar, hacer login como cliente y pegar el token.
@host = http://localhost:3000
@token = <token_cliente>

### 1. Agregar item al carrito -> 200 OK
POST {{host}}/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "<product_id>",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 2. Ver carrito -> 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Agregar otro item -> 200 OK
POST {{host}}/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "<product_id_2>",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 4. Quitar item del carrito -> 200 OK
DELETE {{host}}/api/cart/items/<product_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Vaciar carrito -> 204 No Content
DELETE {{host}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- Casos de error ---

### 6. Acceder sin token -> 401 No autenticado
GET {{host}}/api/cart

### 7. Agregar producto inexistente -> 400 Producto no disponible
POST {{host}}/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 8. Agregar con cantidad inválida -> 400
POST {{host}}/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "<product_id>",
  "quantity": 0
}
